==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inking
<hw>Ink"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Supplying or covering with
ink.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Inking roller</b></col>, <cd>a somewhat elastic roller,
used to spread ink over forms of type, copperplates, etc.</cd> --
<mcol><col><b>Inking trough</b></col> <it>or</it> <col><b>Inking
table</b></col></mcol>, <cd>a trough or table from which the inking
roller receives its ink.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>ink-jet printer</ent>⟦br⟧
